      <h1 class="page-title">Public-private partnerships</h1>
      <div class="breadcrumb-wrapper">
        <ul class="list-inline">
          <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Resources</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Reports</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Public-private partnerships</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{# Intro #}
<section class="intro-wrapper row">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-push-1">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="intro-social text-center">
            <p class="universal-section-desc no-mar-bottom text-center">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent lacinia neque non justo convallis gravida. Etiam vitae tellus volutpat, tristique libero a, porttitor erat. Vivamus convallis, tellus eget commodo malesuada, erat est suscipit neque, quis pellentesque orci leo ut dolor. Proin venenatis non eros ut fringilla. Sed congue elementum semper. Quisque rutrum varius diam.</p>
            <div class="read-more-wrapper text-center">
              <a href="#" class="read-more-btn text-uppercase">View The Report</a>
              <a href="#" class="read-more-btn text-uppercase">Download The Report</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>

{#More Reports section#}
<section class="home-page-news roadmap-resources row">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <h2 class="section-title text-center">More Reports</h2>
      <div class="news-list flex-display">
        {% for i in 1..3 %}
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 flex-display news-item" >
              <a class="news-wrapper" href="#">
                <div class="news-img-wrapper">
                  <img src="/{{ directory }}/assets/images/news/news.jpg" alt="news" class="img-responsive">
                </div>
                <div class="news-content text-center">
                  <h3 class="news-title">Investors Update Guidance to Strengthen Engagement on Climate Risk with Oil and Gas Companies</h3>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="read-more-wrapper text-center">
        <a href="#" class="read-more-btn read-more-effect text-uppercase white-back">More Reports</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{#Sign-up section#}
<div class="row">
  <section class="home-page-signup">
    <img src="/{{ directory }}/assets/images/signup/sign-up.jpg" alt="sign-up" class="img-responsive">
    <div class="container z-index-2 rltv">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-push-1">
          <div class="row">
            <h2 class="section-title text-center">Email Signup</h2>
            <p class="section-desc text-center">Nam suscipit massa condimentum leo aliquet lacinia. Maecenas id felis eget magna placerat dictum non sit amet quam.  Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus.</p>
            <div class="read-more-wrapper text-center">
              <form class="email-signup sign-up-form form-inline" action="/" method="post" accept-charset="UTF-8">
                <div class="form-fields-slide-container form-wrapper">
                  <div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <input placeholder="Last Name" class="required form-control" type="text" name="last_name" value="" size="60" maxlength="150" required="required" aria-required="true">
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <input placeholder="Email" class="required form-control" type="email" name="email" value="" size="60" maxlength="254" required="required" aria-required="true">
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <button class="read-more-btn sign-slide-action subscribr-btn text-uppercase" type="submit" name="op" value="Subscribe">Subscribe</button>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>